  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a young woman who has been caring for her sick father and has been trapped in an anomalous cycle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Observe your surroundings for <strong>anomalies</strong> to find your way out of this nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bring me...</strong>  is a first-person anomaly-horror game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168370/extras/a726aaf6829c46cabe5fd4bca9b437d9.avif?t=1752171696\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a young woman who is forced to care for her sick father. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the story of their bad relationship and how it will end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > His fate is in your hands. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is up to you to decide what to feed him and how to treat him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168370/extras/21906a5061f267b7d7efee23f37ad0da.avif?t=1752171696\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walking simulator with additional mechanics of finding <strong>anomalies</strong> and cooking for your father. Your tasks include:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooking food and preparing medicine</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspecting the house for <strong>anomalies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building a relationship with your father</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168370/extras/048db4f138dc20c57cf9befbc0400748.avif?t=1752171696\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oppressive and unsettling atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 <strong>anomalies</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 game modes (story mode and just search for anomalies)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15-60 minutes</p>",
